#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:2
msgid "## 1. 安装与环境配置"
msgstr "## 1. Installation and Environment Configuration"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:4
msgid "**Q: 如何正确安装 Triton-Ascend？是否支持 pip 直接安装？**"
msgstr "**Q: How to correctly install Triton-Ascend? Does it support direct installation via pip?**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:6
msgid "A: 可以直接使用pip 安装"
msgstr "A: You can directly install it using pip."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:8
msgid ""
"```Python\n"
"pip install triton-ascend\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:10
msgid "**Q: 社区 Triton 和 Triton-Ascend 能否同时存在？**"
msgstr "**Q: Can the community Triton and Triton-Ascend coexist?**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:12
msgid ""
"A: triton-ascend 3.2.0 及以下不可以。需要先卸载社区 Triton，再安装 Triton-Ascend。<br>\n"
"triton-ascend 3.2.1 及以上，Triton-Ascend 通过将 Triton 声明为安装依赖来缓解安装覆盖问题。\n"
"安装 Triton-Ascend 时会先安装社区 Triton，再由 Triton-Ascend 覆盖同名目录，从而避免后续安装其他依赖 Triton 的软件包时再次安装 Triton 而覆盖 Triton-Ascend。\n"
"x86 与 arm 使用不同版本的社区 Triton 安装包的原因是社区从 3.5 版本开始才提供 arm 版本安装包：x86 依赖 triton==3.2.0，arm 依赖 triton==3.5.0。\n"
msgstr ""
"A: For triton-ascend 3.2.0 and below, it is not possible. You need to uninstall the community Triton first, then install Triton-Ascend.<br>\n"
"For triton-ascend 3.2.1 and above, Triton-Ascend mitigates the installation overwrite issue by declaring Triton as an installation dependency.\n"
"When installing Triton-Ascend, the community Triton is installed first, and then Triton-Ascend overwrites the same-named directory, thereby preventing subsequent installations of other software packages that depend on Triton from overwriting Triton-Ascend.\n"
"The reason why x86 and arm use different versions of the community Triton installation package is that the community only provides arm version packages starting from version 3.5: x86 depends on triton==3.2.0, arm depends on triton==3.5.0.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:14
msgid ""
"- 注：若安装triton-ascend后，在安装依赖triton的三方件或者triton本身，将覆盖掉已安装的 Triton-Ascend 目录。\n"
"此时需要先卸载社区 Triton 和 Triton-Ascend，再安装 Triton-Ascend。\n"
msgstr "- Note: If you install a third-party component that depends on triton, or triton itself, after installing triton-ascend, it will overwrite the installed Triton-Ascend directory. In this case, you need to uninstall the community Triton and Triton-Ascend first, and then install Triton-Ascend."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:16
msgid ""
"```Python\n"
"pip uninstall triton\n"
"pip uninstall triton-ascend\n"
"pip install triton-ascend\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:18
msgid "**Q: 能否在非 Ascend 硬件（如 CUDA AMD）上使用 Triton-Ascend？**"
msgstr "**Q: Can Triton-Ascend be used on non-Ascend hardware (such as CUDA AMD)?**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/FAQ.md:20
msgid "A: 不可以，只能在 Ascend NPU 硬件环境使用 Triton-Ascend"
msgstr "A: No, it can only be used in the Ascend NPU hardware environment with Triton-Ascend."

